      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation or equivalent on at least three systematically refined meshes; GCI reported for QoI.",
      "rationale": "Grid convergence study performed on two meshes only; GCI cannot be formally computed. Estimated discretization error on hemolysis index exceeds acceptable threshold at MRL 5."
