      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental boundary conditions match simulated operating points within stated uncertainty bounds for flow rate, rotational speed, and fluid properties.",
      "rationale": "Flow rate and rotational speed are matched; however, blood analogue viscosity deviates from in-vivo values by up to 12%, introducing unquantified bias in shear-stress-driven hemolysis predictions."
