      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric (e.g., E_val) computed with uncertainty; agreement within validation uncertainty band for primary QoI.",
      "rationale": "E_val computed for pressure rise and flow field; hemolysis index comparison is qualitative only. Quantitative agreement criterion not met for the primary safety-relevant QoI."
