      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs used in validation directly correspond to device safety endpoints identified in the intended use specification.",
      "rationale": "Hemolysis index is a recognised surrogate for red blood cell damage but its direct linkage to clinical haemolytic anaemia endpoints is not formally documented in this assessment."
